name: Jenna Franquelin
coverLetter:
I have a little bit of a background in trimming, I've trimmed here and there over the last 2-3 years. Have experience with a variety of strains. I am passionate to learn more, and become more educated about trimming and about cannabis in general. I live in Arcata (Humboldt county), and am just looking for a part-time job, but especially wanting to work in an industry I am most passionate about -- this industry! Trimming is absolutely one of my favorite tasks to do. A hard-working, passionate, team-player who is ready to learn more about cannabis and trimming, and will  do everything in her power to do her job extremely well.
Availability: 
Tuesday- Free all day except for a class from 2-5 pm (able to work before and/or after this time frame)
Thursday- Available all day
Friday- Available after 11:45 pm
Saturday- Available all day
Sunday- Available all day
